George Papandreou on the developments in the Balkans and relations
between Montenegro and Serbia.
</P>
<P>
The two men also discussed possibilities for the upgrade of
bilateral relations, closer relations between Montenegro and the
European Union (EU), as well as the democratization of Serbia and
the relations of Serbia with the rest of the world.
</P>
