Yugoslavia, but its relationship with Serbia should allow for the
autonomous development of Montenegro.
</P>
<P>
Montenegro, one of Yugoslavia's two republics, has reportedly
proposed a new relationship with Serbia, which includes a separate
currency, defense and Foreign Ministries.
</P>
<P>
On Tuesday, Djukanovic will meet with Greek Prime Minister
Costas Simitis. 
