<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, August 30 (Xinhua) -- The United Nations
Development Program (UNDP) and the Global Environment Facility
have launched a 20 million U.S. dollar program to help Malaysia
reduce emissions of greenhouse gases, the UNDP said Monday.
