year-long civil war in Democratic Congo can be ended at long last.
</P>
<P>
Zambian President Federick Chiluba sponsored the signing
ceremony at the Inter-continental hotel here with ministers from
the 14-nation Southern African Development Community (SADC), as
well as Rwanda and Uganda who had supported the rebels, attending
the function.
</P>
<P>
