area of hostilities," Sergeyev said.
</P>
<P>
Interfax, quoting Russian military experts, said several
hundred militants are entrenched in southwest Kyrgyzstan and are
holding a number of hostages, including the commander of the
Kyrgyz Interior Troops and four Japanese geologists. 
