<HEADLINE> Sino-Ecuadorian Friendship Hailed (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mahuad described his visit as having achieved satisfactory
results because the two countries have signed a series of
important cooperation documents, which will spur the two-way trade
and cement the friendship between the peoples of the two countries.
</P>
<P>
Referring to the relations between the parliaments of the two
countries, Li said that their respective legislatures have
maintained friendly exchanges, which constitute an important part
of bilateral ties.
</P>
<P>
Recent years have witnessed the efforts of the two parliaments
to further the understanding and friendship between them, he added.
</P>
<P>
